Package: rmdocs
Title: Open R help files in RMarkdown format  
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Miles",
           family = "McBain",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "miles.mcbain@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: Open R Help files in RMarkdown format in a new editor tab. 
    Includes an RStudio addin to do this for the current selection or word cursor is on.
    Compatible with RStudio and VSCode.
